    \"<span class=sf-dump-key>description</span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1264 characters\">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(13, 13, 13); font-family: S&#246;hne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Arial, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Color Emoji&amp;quot;; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;Discover ultimate comfort and sophistication with our exquisite collection of luxury corner and 2+3 seater sofas. Crafted with precision and attention to detail, each piece embodies elegance and refinement, elevating your living space to new heights of luxury. Sink into sumptuous cushions and experience unparalleled relaxation as you unwind after a long day. Our corner sofas offer versatility, maximizing your living room space, while the 2+3 seater sets provide ample seating for family and guests. Choose from a range of premium fabrics and finishes to complement your interior d&#233;cor effortlessly. Whether you prefer classic designs or modern aesthetics, our collection caters to every style preference. Indulge in the epitome of luxury living with our meticulously curated selection of sofas, designed to enhance your home&#039;s ambiance and make a statement of sophistication&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span>\"
